### Sipariş listesi — konsolda structured log gör
GET http://localhost:5155/api/orders
Accept: application/json

### Sipariş detayı — nested span gör
GET http://localhost:5155/api/orders/1
Accept: application/json

### Olmayan sipariş — warning log gör
GET http://localhost:5155/api/orders/999
Accept: application/json

### Sipariş oluştur — success log gör
POST http://localhost:5155/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerName": "Ahmet Yılmaz",
  "totalAmount": 299.99
}

### Geçersiz tutar — validation warning gör
POST http://localhost:5155/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerName": "Test",
  "totalAmount": -1
}